/// NRSI — Unified Cognitive Bridge.
///
/// Wires ALL reasoning layers into a single cognitive pipeline:
///
/// Perception:   SemanticQueryParser
/// Attention:    SpreadingActivation
/// Memory:       CausalGraph + CommonSense + ConversationalLearner
/// Inference:    InferenceEngine + AbductiveReasoner + CounterfactualReasoner
///               + DeductionEngine + ConstraintPropagator
/// Knowledge:    TemporalReasoner + QuantitativeReasoner
/// Social:       SocialCognition
/// Planning:     GoalPlanner
/// Learning:     ConversationalLearner + BayesianUpdater
/// Governance:   KnowledgeIngestionGate + GraphMaintenance
/// Confidence:   GraphConfidenceManager
/// Language:     GroundedGenerator (zero-hallucination)
/// Epistemic:    EpistemicEngine
/// Coherence:    CoherenceController
/// Synthesis:    ReasoningSynthesizer
/// Adversarial:  AdversarialSelfTester
/// Provenance:   ProvenanceTracker
///
/// All transformer-free.

